OL,3,CRotherham grooming scandal: Seven men
OL,4,Cconvicted of abusing girls
OL,6,FThe court heard how the attacks took
OL,7,Fplace at locations around Rotherham,
OL,8,Fincluding a park, in a supermarket car
OL,9,Fpark, a cemetery and behind a
OL,10,Fchildren's nursery.JIn one case one of
OL,11,Fthe girls was taken to a hotel where
OL,12,Fshe was raped by two men. On another
OL,13,Foccasion the same girl was locked
OL,14,Finside one of her abuser's homes,
OL,15,Fraped on at least two occasions, and
OL,16,Fonly managed to escape by climbing out
OL,17,Fof a window.
