OL,3,CRotherham grooming scandal: Seven men
OL,4,Cconvicted of abusing girls
OL,6,FThe gang were arrested as part of
OL,7,FOperation Stovewood ` a National Crime
OL,8,FAgency (NCA) investigation into child
OL,9,Fsexual abuse in Rotherham between 1997
OL,10,Fand 2013.
OL,12,FThe seven defendants were found guilty
OL,13,Ffollowing a nine-week trial.
OL,15,FZoe Becker, of the Crown Prosecution
OL,16,FService, said: "These seven men knew
OL,17,Fthat these young girls could be
OL,18,Fexploited ` they targeted the victims
OL,19,Fand, using drugs and alcohol, groomed
OL,20,Fthem for sex.
