OL,3,CRotherham grooming scandal: Seven men
OL,4,Cconvicted of abusing girls
OL,6,F"These defendants waged a campaign of
OL,7,Fviolence against the two girls, who
OL,8,Fhad to endure some of the most
OL,9,Ftraumatic abuse on multiple occasions."
OL,11,FThe guilty verdicts mean that 33
OL,12,Fpeople have now been convicted of
OL,13,Foffences uncovered by Operation
OL,14,FStovewood.
OL,16,FThe operation is the single largest
OL,17,Finvestigation of its kind in the UK,
OL,18,Fwith more than 1,150 potential victims
OL,19,Fidentified.
