OL,3,CRotherham grooming scandal: Seven men
OL,4,Cconvicted of abusing girls
OL,6,FNCA senior investigating officer
OL,7,FStuart Cobb said: "The evidence we
OL,8,Fheard from these victims was some of
OL,9,Fthe most harrowing we have come
OL,10,Facross, and the offences involved some
OL,11,Fof the most serious yet investigated
OL,12,Fby officers working on Operation
OL,13,FStovewood.
OL,15,F"I pay tribute to the bravery of these
OL,16,Ftwo victims in coming forward and
OL,17,Ftelling their stories. It was key to
OL,18,Fgetting these convictions and I hope
OL,19,Fthey feel that justice has finally
OL,20,Fbeen done.
