OL,3,CRotherham grooming scandal: Seven men
OL,4,Cconvicted of abusing girls
OL,6,F"What happened to them was appalling.
OL,7,FTheir attackers were cruel,
OL,8,Fmanipulative men, who thought it was
OL,9,Ffine to take advantage of vulnerable
OL,10,Fyoung girls and dehumanise their
OL,11,Fvictims in the worst possible ways."
OL,13,FThe seven men will be sentenced on 12
OL,14,Fand 13 September.
OL,16,FAbid Saddiq is already serving a 20-
OL,17,Fyear prison sentence having been
OL,18,Fconvicted in 2019 of sexual offences.
